  <title>Layer filtering TOC view</title>
  <purpose>This sample shows an implementation of a custom table of contents (TOC) view that shows a tree view with map layers filtered by the layer type specified in a combo box. This sample also shows how to bring up an appropriate context menu when the data frame or layer tree node is right-clicked in the custom TOC.</purpose>
